    <constitutionalAuthorityStatementText><![CDATA[<pre>From the Congressional Record Online through the Government Publishing Office [<a href='http://www.gpo.gov'>www.gpo.gov</a>]By Mr. SCHIFF:H.J. Res. 58.Congress has the power to enact this legislation pursuantto the following:Congress has the power to enact this legislation pursuantto Article V of the United States Constitution.____________________[Page H4651]</pre>]]></constitutionalAuthorityStatementText>
